description: This file contains platform-independent utility functions for creating an HTTP Mbo File object, including the definition of the function HttpCreateMboFile which calls HttpMboFileCreate to instantiate the object. It also includes license and copyright information.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE HttpCreateMboFile(ANSC_HANDLE hContainerContext,ANSC_HANDLE hOwnerContext,ANSC_HANDLE hAnscReserved)
methods.description: Creates and returns a new Http Mbo File object by invoking HttpMboFileCreate with the provided context handles.
